data.description: Wow! 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath home on large corner lot with split Bedroom floorplan, - with 2 Bedrooms on one end & 2 Bedrooms upstairs, with full Bath upstairs too.  Main level includes living room with full wall gorgeous fireplace & mantel. Kitchen & dining room & full bath.  Lower level has a spacious family room, plus storage & workshop area. Front of home has a covered patio area & Enclosed Sunroom to greet you. Home has an Privacy wood fence in back yard, 2 1/2 car garage in side yard w/power(separate electrical panel in garage (100 amp),  Plus a newer shed in side yard too. Don't miss out on this one.
